description_of_request:
ASTI Environmental is conducting an environmental assessment for a property in Chicago, IL and respectfully request any
Assessing Department records regarding historical and current assessing records and field sheets;
Building Department records regarding any building permits, site plans, sketches, code violations, and inspections;
Zoning Department: records regarding permits and maps; and
Fire Department records regarding any reports of spills/releases, above ground and underground storage tanks, landfilling, fires, code violations, and Hazmat incidents.
Environmental Health: records regarding well/septic, landfilling activity, spills/releases, 201 sites, ASTs, USTs, or other environmental concerns.

Work History for all years that David Moore was an employee of the City of Chicago, to include salaries, salary increases, departments worked, etc.
The names and salaries of the staff employed (regular payroll and contractor/voucher staff) by the 17th Ward budget line item starting April 2015 to the present;
Non Personnel Expenditures for any financial outflows from Ward 17 accounts (017 or finance general Dept 99) from April 2015 to the present;
Aldermanic menu item expenditures for Ward 17 projects (location, amount, type) from April 2015 to the present
